ALL.doc: ALL(MASK) returns .TRUE. if all elements of MASK are true; also true for zero-size arrays. [F90]

ANY.doc: ANY(MASK) returns .TRUE. if any element of MASK is true; returns .FALSE. for zero-size arrays. [F90]

COUNT.doc: COUNT(MASK) returns the number of .TRUE. elements in logical array MASK. [F90]

MAXVAL.doc: MAXVAL(ARRAY) returns maximum value of array elements; returns -HUGE(ARRAY) for empty sets. [F90]

MINVAL.doc: MINVAL(ARRAY) returns minimum value of array elements; returns HUGE(ARRAY) for empty sets. [F90]

PRODUCT.doc: PRODUCT(ARRAY) returns product of all array elements; returns 1 for zero-size arrays. [F90]

SUM.doc: SUM(ARRAY) returns sum of all array elements; returns 0 for zero-size arrays. [F90]
